data.description: OH MY GOODNESS!  PRICE CORRECTED DOWN TO $363,000!! LENNAR 'Everything is Included Home' in gorgeous Cape Coral. You won't go wrong with this amazing home. So close to the Gulf, and several new homes being built in that area. Only 15 minutes to Matlacha, 20 minutes to Pine Island, 42 minutes to Fort Myers Beach and 48 minutes to Sanibel! Many dining & shopping options close by. Beautiful tones and an easy layout in this home. Move In ready and please bring your pet - there is a fully fenced back yard. LARGE Primary en-Suite plus 2 additional bedrooms and another full bath for your guests. It's time for a new home and THIS IS IT!
